text: Wise County is a county in the U.S. state of Texas. In 2020, 68,632 people lived there. The county seat is Decatur. ==History== The county was created in 1856. ==Geography== The county has a total area of 923 square miles. ==Places== ===Cities=== * Aurora * Bridgeport * Chico * Decatur (county seat) * Lake Bridgeport ===Towns=== * Alvord * Boyd ==References==
title: Wise County, Texas
